Interesting thing to note (specifically for things like tails / cables), if you select multiple points on the model, and try to rotate them all at once in SFM, if you're in the motion editor, it only rotates the root selection
But if you try rotating them in the timeline editor, it'll rotate all points at the same time for the same amount.
